rows.label: tev057101_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev057101_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Jalolo about the Nopon.

rows.label: tev057101_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev057101_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Jalolo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Jalolo what things were like during the attack.

rows.label: tev057101_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Jalolo about the Zu Pharg.

rows.label: tev057101_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Jalolo about business.

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0001
rows.name:
Money is most important thing to Nopon.
But signed IOU is next best thing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0002
rows.name:
Nopon know better than to take each other at word.
That just BEGS for trouble![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0003
rows.name: Better to get every little detail in writing instead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0004
rows.name:
Jalolo can be real sleazeball when situation calls
for it, but friend will never catch Jalolo lying on paper!
If Jalolo write it down, it is legit![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0008
rows.name:
How come girlypon fall for THAT pathetic pauper,
anyway? Meeeeeh! Jalolo is displeased![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0009
rows.name:
Welcome to Moneylender Jalolo! Interest normally
start at 50 percent every 10 days, but Jalolo having
bad day, so make it 80 percent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0010
rows.name:
Actually, friend not look nearly trustworthy enough to
borrow money. So scram![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0015
rows.name:
Jalolo see it all! Whole load of Ganglion fly south,
then return north some time later.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0016
rows.name:
Jalolo can be real sleazeball when situation calls
for it, but seriously?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0017
rows.name:
Jalolo has NOTHING on group as evil and ominous
and scary as those guys...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0018
rows.name:
Maybe Jalolo should approach Ganglion with deal
now and get on good side while still possible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0023
rows.name:
Jalolo thought he discovered first ever moving
mountain, but it was actually Ganglion weapon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0024
rows.name:
This made Jalolo wonder if making deals with such
dangerous customers was smart idea.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0025
rows.name:
But human friends who defeated big evil weapon must
be even scarier, and Jalolo made deals with them...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0026
rows.name:
Maybe Jalolo needs to finally pick side for own safety.
But which one? Hmm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0030
rows.name: Meh! Jalolo does not have future as psychic.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0031
rows.name:
Jalolo was certain human friends would lose and
decided to deal exclusively with Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0032
rows.name:
Nothing personal, friend. Business is business.
And besides, Jalolo got what was coming to him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0033
rows.name:
Now that Ganglion is destroyed, Jalolo is massively
in debt![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0034
rows.name:
But human friend should not feel guilty.
Jalolo have no one to blame but self.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Jalolo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0011
rows.name: Jalolo was VERY certain that Nio handed over tuft![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0012
rows.name:
So how did Nio grow new tuft so fast, hmm?
And why are he and girlypon getting on so well?
Even stupid ring look nice on her![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0013
rows.name:
Mgrrr... No! Jalolo is NOT okay with this!
If Nio and girlypon plan to live here, Jalolo is going
to spend every second making their lives hell![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev057101_MSG0014
rows.name: Jalolo refuses to be the only one without happiness![ST:wait ]
